Package de.cuioss.test.jsf.mocks

Class CuiMockSearchExpressionContextFactory

java.lang.Object
javax.faces.component.search.SearchExpressionContextFactory
de.cuioss.test.jsf.mocks.CuiMockSearchExpressionContextFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
FacesWrapper<SearchExpressionContextFactory>
public class CuiMockSearchExpressionContextFactory extends SearchExpressionContextFactory
Mock for SearchExpressionContextFactory. It can be used by accessing the instance of the mock by using retrieve() and setting a concrete #setSearchExpressionContext(SearchExpressionContext) that is used for the actual test. If not an instance of CuiMockSearchExpressionContext will be returned.
Author:
Oliver Wolff
